oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ronnie Reno Studio Recordings
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Ronnie Reno (musician). The recording features Ronnie Reno performing: "Costs a Lot to be Alone," "Some of the Places," "You've Gone too Far This Time," "I Can't Find That Feelin,'" "Hay Fever," "Home Again," "Take the Time," "Dangerous Love," and "Somethin' From Nothin.'" Recordings are from a variety of unidentified dates.
